	receiving the highest number of affirmative votes of all the votes properly cast shall be elected as Class II directors to serve until the 2020 Annual Meeting of Stockholders or until their successors have been duly elected and qualified.



	Recommendation of the Board of Directors




	The Board of Directors recommends that the stockholders vote FOR the election of the two (2) Class II nominees listed above.



	 


