	Required Vote



	The ratification of the selection of KPMG LLP requires the affirmative vote of a majority of the votes cast on the proposal at the Annual
	Meeting (meaning the number of shares voted for the proposal must exceed the number of shares voted against the proposal). Abstentions are not considered votes cast for the foregoing purpose, and will have no effect on the
	vote for this proposal.



	Recommendation of the Board of Directors




	The Board of Directors recommends that the stockholders vote FOR the ratification of the appointment of KPMG LLP as the independent
	registered public accounting firm of the Company for its fiscal year ending December 31, 2017.



	 


